<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q48_v2" title="Q48_v2" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>Los números 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>64</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo>
          <m:mn>72</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo>
          <m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo>
          <m:mn>88</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo>
          <m:mi>x</m:mi>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      tienen un promedio de 
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>78</m:mn>
      </m:math>.
      Se sabe que x es uno de los siguientes valores. ¿Cuál de ellos puede ser el valor de x?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>78</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>78</m:mn></m:math>, entonces la suma total sería <m:math><m:mn>64</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>72</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>88</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>78</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>382</m:mn></m:math>. Pero para que el promedio de 5 números sea 78, la suma debe ser <m:math><m:mn>78</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>390</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>382</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>390</m:mn></m:math>, esta opción no puede ser el valor de <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>76</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>76</m:mn></m:math>, entonces la suma total sería <m:math><m:mn>64</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>72</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>88</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>76</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>380</m:mn></m:math>. Pero para que el promedio de 5 números sea 78, la suma debe ser <m:math><m:mn>78</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>390</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>380</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>390</m:mn></m:math>, esta opción no puede ser el valor de <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>86</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! La suma de los cuatro números conocidos es <m:math><m:mn>64</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>72</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>88</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>304</m:mn></m:math>. Como el promedio de 5 números es 78, la suma total debe ser <m:math><m:mn>78</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>390</m:mn></m:math>. Entonces <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>390</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>304</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>86</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>82</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>82</m:mn></m:math>, entonces la suma total sería <m:math><m:mn>64</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>72</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>88</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>82</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>386</m:mn></m:math>. Pero para que el promedio de 5 números sea 78, la suma debe ser <m:math><m:mn>78</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>390</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>386</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>390</m:mn></m:math>, esta opción no puede ser el valor de <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Sumar los números conocidos</strong></p>
            <p>Los cuatro números conocidos son 64, 72, 80 y 88.</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>64</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>72</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>88</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>304</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Usar el promedio para encontrar la suma total</strong></p>
            <p>Hay 5 números en total y su promedio es 78.</p>
            <p>Entonces, la suma total debe ser:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>78</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>390</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Restar para hallar el valor de x</strong></p>
            <p>Como la suma de los cuatro números conocidos es 304, el valor faltante es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>390</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>304</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>86</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa que coincide con el valor obtenido es 86.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El valor de <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> puede ser <strong>86</strong>, es decir, la alternativa <strong>C</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>